{
  "info": {
    "name": "Mini Mercado Livre — payment-service",
    "_postman_id": "f7a8b9c0-d1e2-3456-fa12-345678901bcd",
    "description": "API de pagamentos do Mini Mercado Livre.\nBase URL: {{base_url}} (default: http://localhost:8083)\n\nAutenticação: Bearer JWT no header Authorization.\nUse a variável {{token}} com o access_token obtido do Keycloak.\n\n⚠️ Pagamentos NÃO são criados via API — são gerados automaticamente pelo\nconsumer Kafka ao receber order.created.v1 do order-service.\n\nFluxo para testar o ciclo completo:\n1. Suba o order-service (porta 8082) e crie um pedido\n2. O payment-service consome o evento Kafka e processa o pagamento\n3. Use esta collection para consultar o resultado\n\nRegra de aprovação mock:\n  • amount ≤ R$ 50.000,00 → AUTHORIZED (publica payment.authorized.v1)\n  • amount >  R$ 50.000,00 → FAILED    (publica payment.failed.v1)\n\nFluxo sugerido:\n1. Pre-request script auto-obtém token do Keycloak\n2. Consultar por orderId (01) — preenche {{ultimo_payment_id}} e {{ultimo_order_id}}\n3. Consultar por paymentId (02)\n4. Listar todos (05), por customer (06), por status (07)\n5. Testar erros 401/404 (03, 04, 08)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8083",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Access token JWT. Preenchido automaticamente pelo Pre-request Script da collection."
    },
    {
      "key": "ultimo_payment_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Preenchido automaticamente ao consultar /payments/order/{orderId}"
    },
    {
      "key": "ultimo_order_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Cole aqui o UUID de um pedido criado no order-service para testar o fluxo"
    },
    {
      "key": "ultimo_customer_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Auto-renova o token JWT antes de cada request",
          "const tokenUrl = 'http://localhost:8080/realms/mini-mercado-livre/protocol/openid-connect/token';",
          "const currentToken = pm.collectionVariables.get('token');",
          "",
          "// Só busca novo token se não houver um definido",
          "if (!currentToken) {",
          "    pm.sendRequest({",
          "        url: tokenUrl,",
          "        method: 'POST',",
          "        header: { 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' },",
          "        body: {",
          "            mode: 'urlencoded',",
          "            urlencoded: [",
          "                { key: 'grant_type', value: 'password' },",
          "                { key: 'client_id',  value: 'mini-ml-frontend' },",
          "                { key: 'username',   value: 'user1' },",
          "                { key: 'password',   value: 'user1pass' }",
          "            ]",
          "        }",
          "    }, (err, res) => {",
          "        if (!err && res.json().access_token) {",
          "            pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.json().access_token);",
          "        }",
          "    });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Pagamentos",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "01 — Buscar pagamento por orderId (200)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const oid = pm.collectionVariables.get('ultimo_order_id');",
                  "if (!oid) {",
                  "    console.warn('Variável ultimo_order_id não definida.');",
                  "    console.warn('Cole o UUID de um pedido criado no order-service.');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', () => {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Retorna campos obrigatórios', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('id');",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('orderId');",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('customerId');",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('amount');",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('currency');",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('status');",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('paymentMethod');",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('createdAt');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('currency é BRL', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().currency).to.equal('BRL');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('status é AUTHORIZED ou FAILED', () => {",
                  "    const status = pm.response.json().status;",
                  "    pm.expect(['AUTHORIZED', 'FAILED']).to.include(status);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('paymentMethod é CREDIT_CARD (mock)', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().paymentMethod).to.equal('CREDIT_CARD');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "// Salva IDs para requests seguintes",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body.id) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('ultimo_payment_id', body.id);",
                  "    console.log('Payment ID:', body.id, '| Status:', body.status);",
                  "}",
                  "if (body.customerId) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('ultimo_customer_id', body.customerId);",
                  "}",
                  "if (body.orderId) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('ultimo_order_id', body.orderId);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/payments/order/{{ultimo_order_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["payments", "order", "{{ultimo_order_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Busca o pagamento vinculado a um pedido.\nPreencha a variável 'ultimo_order_id' com o UUID de um pedido do order-service."
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "02 — Buscar pagamento por paymentId (200)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', () => {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('ID corresponde ao solicitado', () => {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    const expectedId = pm.collectionVariables.get('ultimo_payment_id');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.id).to.equal(expectedId);",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('orderId');",
                  "    pm.expect(body).to.have.property('amount');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.amount).to.be.above(0);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/payments/{{ultimo_payment_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["payments", "{{ultimo_payment_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Busca pelo ID do próprio pagamento (preenchido automaticamente pelo request 01)."
          }
        },

